title: 2016 Week 3 Review
itunes:title: 2016 Week 3 Review
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – recap all the games from the third Sunday of the regular season including Trevor Siemian leading the Broncos to victory over the Bengals and the Buffalo Bills taking down Carson Palmer’s Cardinals. Then the heroes break down the Sunday Night Football game where Ezekiel Elliott and the Cowboys defeated the Brian Hoyer led Chicago Bears.
